Category:  Skills  Topic:  bodyslam



This skill is pretty spectacular and does a good ammount of damage.  It
can also stun the victim for up to 4 rounds of battle.

Syntax:  bodyslam <i_th> <victim>

Example:  bodyslam	     // attempt to slam whoever you are fighting
	  bodyslam 2.guard   // slam the second guard

See Also:  bash, skills
